data.description: Stunning residence located on a corner lot! Step inside to discover  a kitchen equipped w/all appliances. Entertain guests in the charming living room or host casual gatherings in the x-large dining room. Working from home is a cinch w/a dedicated office space. The exterior incl. built-in LED lighting-perfect for that holiday or team color glow! Escape to the privacy of your bedroom, featuring a balcony where you can unwind. Your pool is a great entertainment arena w/a water feature & LED lighting. Above ground hot tub conveys! Love the great outdoors? Included is RV parking & ample space for your adventurous spirit. No off property storage needed! New roof/2019, new A/C in 2022. Solar Panels new in 2019 and are owned.
